{"words":[{"word":"general","count":5},{"word":"first","count":4},{"word":"relay","count":3},{"word":"race","count":3},{"word":"jiyan","count":3},{"word":"starting","count":2},{"word":"join","count":2},{"word":"best","count":2},{"word":"playername","count":2},{"word":"order","count":2},{"word":"soon","count":1},{"word":"impossible","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"another","count":1},{"word":"person","count":1},{"word":"mention","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"sigh","count":1},{"word":"captain","count":1},{"word":"quit","count":1},{"word":"family","count":1},{"word":"emergency","count":1},{"word":"ugh","count":1},{"word":"supposed","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"riverside","count":1},{"word":"games","count":1},{"word":"knows","count":1},{"word":"buy","count":1},{"word":"barbecue","count":1},{"word":"jinzhou","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"everyone's","count":1},{"word":"favorite","count":1},{"word":"wh-who","count":1},{"word":"huh","count":1},{"word":"serious","count":1},{"word":"interested","count":1},{"word":"events","count":1},{"word":"guts","count":1},{"word":"managed","count":1},{"word":"rope","count":1},{"word":"hooray","count":1},{"word":"side","count":1},{"word":"maybe","count":1},{"word":"aim","count":1},{"word":"new","count":1},{"word":"record","count":1},{"word":"unless","count":1},{"word":"yeah","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"wanted","count":1},{"word":"learn","count":1},{"word":"strategy","count":1},{"word":"video","count":1},{"word":"borrowed","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"returned","count":1},{"word":"bummer","count":1},{"word":"wow","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"worry","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"left","count":1},{"word":"decided","count":1},{"word":"seriously","count":1},{"word":"whew","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"followed","count":1},{"word":"lingyan","count":1},{"word":"last","count":1},{"word":"yes","count":1},{"word":"team","count":1},{"word":"name","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1},{"word":"crave","count":1},{"word":"buffalo","count":1},{"word":"wings","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"But the relay is starting soon. It's impossible to find another person to join us, not to mention two...","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Sigh... First our captain had to quit because of some family emergency, and now this...","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Ugh. Are we supposed to just wait for the next Riverside Games? Who knows when that will be...","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"That's right! We'll buy you the best barbecue in Jinzhou. That place is everyone's favorite!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Wh-who?","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"!!!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Huh? Are you serious? The general doesn't look like he'd be interested in events like this.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"I don't have the guts...","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"You... You managed to rope the general in?","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Hooray! Now we can join the race! With General Jiyan and {PlayerName} on our side, maybe we can even aim for a new record!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Unless what?","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Yeah! I really wanted to learn from their strategy, but the video of that race got borrowed and never returned. Bummer.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Wow, so even General Jiyan has heard of that race!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"We should worry about ourselves first... There's not much time left, and we haven't even decided the relay order.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Me... the first? Seriously?","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Whew—I'll do my best.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Then the relay order would be me first, followed by Lingyan, then General Jiyan, and {PlayerName} last.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Yes!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Our team doesn't have a name yet!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"I'm starting to crave some buffalo wings too...","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080}]}